lumis.doui.source.field.type

Class SourceFieldTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • lumis.doui.source.field.type.SourceFieldTypes

  • public class SourceFieldTypes
extends Object
    Framework doui source field data types. Contains contants for the data types ids and a factory method for obtaining data type instances.
